# shadcn UI Usage

This project uses **shadcn UI** for all UI elements.

## Initial Setup

If shadcn UI is not initialized in the project, use the following command:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest create
```

## Adding Components

To install a specific component (e.g., button component), use:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

Replace `button` with the name of any component you need to install.

## General Guidelines

- Always use shadcn UI components for all UI elements
- Do not create custom UI components when a shadcn UI equivalent exists
- Check the shadcn UI documentation for available components before building custom solutions
